surveying the crowd peter tse a real estate agent for an 
australian company heaved a sigh 
theres a sucker born every minute he said im just 
selling houses but the consultants theyre exploiting fear 
indeed in the immigration industry consultants are the big 
moneymakers charging as much as 50000 for a successful case 
consultants help prospective emigrants fill out forms draw up 
business proposals and determine whether they have the necessary 
credentials to emigrate 
since january the ranks of hong kongbased consultants have 
swollen to 600 a 100 percent jump according to alex lee an 
